title: Turn Off Your Brain, Just Act
itunes:title: Turn Off Your Brain, Just Act
description:
Episode 578 - Are you an overthinker? Do you think too much about what you need to do and that gets in the way of taking action? In this episode I am going to teach you how to turn off you brain, get to work and create the life that you want to create.
